{"tid":2068353,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"贊成山本彩留返長頭髮既入","createTime":"2020-06-17T15:18:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-17T16:22:41.000Z","uid":322267,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"146928300ce5cedda39de5a40989eb87183b0acd","tid":2068353,"uid":322267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:18:52.000Z","msg":"長髮彩姐真係好好丁，特別teacher teacher個look<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"043518156e29c2bad347836e3cbcb40e2ba1026a","tid":2068353,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:19:30.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借位一用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">[全人類請入] 投訴蘇文隆 唔好再俾條粉皮害手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2068154\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2068154</a></span></span></strong><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rNPeQ2w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrNPeQ2w.jpg&h=f4a8a3f6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/suBXOPc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsuBXOPc.jpg&h=39c942dc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EdP2ZVS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEdP2ZVS.png&h=1bd9e71b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有人會話法治已經死咗好撚耐<br />\n做呢啲嘢有撚用咩<br />\n<br />\n我唔知道做咗又冇用<br />\n我淨係知唔做就一定乜嘢都冇<br />\n<br />\n之前情操高尚嗰條粉皮暫時都冇得再審政治案件<br />\n都係多得各位手足堅持寫信投訴<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果唔想香港好嘅社工越來越少<br />\n如果唔想香港未來<br />\n得返一啲淨係識得幫新賤民呃公屋嘅社畜<br />\n如果唔想香港未來<br />\n未成年手足被藍屍社工出賣</span></span><br />\n唔該一人一信<br />\n保護一個為咗愛我地而失去左一年光陰<br />\n為咗愛香港而冒着釘牌危機都要行出嚟<br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好懶<br />\n依家輪到我哋愛佢了"},{"pid":"eb7998b4414e5fcdf8b3b4fe43a36284e0f48b55","tid":2068353,"uid":12782,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:30:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hLTOVS5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhLTOVS5.gif&h=ecead620&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n畢業單先最正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1786e831400700d9e92f7390d2c14dbba09f38b","tid":2068353,"uid":66346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:38:01.000Z","msg":"長短都正<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2f447ce9962600d5fd28587e1b3810518caee8c","tid":2068353,"uid":24361,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:46:11.000Z","msg":"長頭髮可以扯住條馬尾狗仔式"},{"pid":"43964ecbcd92bdd984ba2be1eb6f9572c7f9c236","tid":2068353,"uid":322267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb7998b4414e5fcdf8b3b4fe43a36284e0f48b55","tid":2068353,"uid":12782,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:30:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hLTOVS5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhLTOVS5.gif&h=ecead620&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n畢業單先最正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T16:18:52.000Z","msg":"最鐘意佢set少少攣或者紮馬尾少攣，好有女人味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee9232c4f6cd81c7e0729003494e4a8f96b0cddc","tid":2068353,"uid":322267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2f447ce9962600d5fd28587e1b3810518caee8c","tid":2068353,"uid":24361,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:46:11.000Z","msg":"長頭髮可以扯住條馬尾狗仔式"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T16:21:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"